---
import { AppConfig } from "../../data";
---

<section class="Slide">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 class="title">Messaging Pillars</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <ol class="grid-ol">
                <li>
                    <span>Growth First, Always</span>
                    <span>Every solution { AppConfig.brand_name } builds is anchored to a business outcome you can measure. Not a deliverable you store on a hard drive — a result you can see in your numbers.</span>
                    <span class="text-xs italic">"If it doesn't grow your business, we don't build it."</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Technology Made Human</span>
                    <span>We translate complex digital systems into plain English and practical action. You'll always know what's being built, why it's being built that way, and what to expect when it's live.</span>
                    <span class="text-xs italic">"We handle the tech. You focus on your business."</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Built for the Global Market</span>
                    <span>We understand the Global market — its pace, its constraints, its massive potential. Our solutions aren't imported templates. They're built for where you actually are, to grow you to where you want to be.</span>
                    <span class="text-xs italic">"Global quality. Real results."</span>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
